Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school student Shinichi was forced\Nto take a drug that shrunk him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.59,0:00:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case involves a\NJune bride dressed in white!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with her happiness about to crumble,\Nthere's always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The June Bride Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, a middle school teacher\Nthat Ran and I had is getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm definitely not here for her sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to see the wacko\Nwho's marrying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto-sensei... I haven't\Nseen her since we graduated!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we'll get to hear her amazing\Nsinging voice at the reception!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, what about you-know-who?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the kid who would\Nalways get yelled at
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for being off key in\NMatsumoto-sensei's music class...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called him but he said wouldn't go\Neven if his life depended on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you brought this kid\Nwith you instead of Mr. Tone-Deaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! He insisted on coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for being tone-deaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That lousy woman did nothing\Nbut torture me for three full years!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Mori-san and Suzuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Does it look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You look beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She does...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Waiting Room"\NAw, Kudo-kun can't make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I wanted to show off this dress\Nin front of that impertinent brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't changed at all on the inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met before, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Look this way, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in charge of the video for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure the kiss scene\Nis a really great one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought you your warm lemon tea, Sayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, she was always\Ndrinking lemon tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even during class...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Your lipstick will come off\Nif you drink it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazumi... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Toshihiko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking\Nabout at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better be ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna tell everyone at the reception
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that your new hubby\Nused to be my boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you in a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never stops teasing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bad friend of mine from college.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have another can,\Nwould one of you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Beat this gorilla's brains out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? If it isn't Ran-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure!\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in their right mind would miss\Ntheir boss's daughter's wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. He's the police\Nsuperintendent and my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his fault for looking so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Sayuri, are you really sure\Nyou want to marry him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have young men with plenty\Nof backbone working for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! What are you saying\Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really now! You always have to\Ntreat me like a child, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still drink this sugary rubbish...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?! I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how about saying something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at what your daughter is wearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beautiful. Though not nearly\Nas beautiful as your dead mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you ever give a normal compliment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What beautiful roses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Umemiya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember? That's Umemiya-san--\Nhe was one year ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon tea suits you well,\NMatsumoto-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is a real disappointment for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always believed that only I\Ncould ever make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umemiya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a conceited jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! The battery's almost out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't there an\Nelectronics store near here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you'd think to at least check\Nthat before leaving the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look exactly like Kudo Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking at your face\Nmakes me want to pinch you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:07:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Kudo-kun looked\Njust like my very first boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His family ran the\Nneighborhood candy store,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and whenever someone was bullying me,\Nhe'd always come to my rescue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would always secretly steal\Nmy favorite drink from his own store
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and give it to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warm lemon tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to forget those memories,\NI still drink it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like it gives me courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was the reason I was\Ntormented for three long years?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So does he still live there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. One day, he suddenly moved away,\Nand I've never seen him since.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's more to this story...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you being so\Nshy about? You're the groom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshihiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look stunning, Sayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just our little secret, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still drinking this cheap filth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the successor\Nto the Takasugi Group!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You're one of\Nthose Suzuki plutocrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see him at parties all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's indecisive and undependable,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and people say that the Takasugi family's\Ngoing to end with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that come from\Nall of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's with him,\Nso I think he'll be all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt, but it's\Nalmost time for the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on ahead, Toshihiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll be there soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how's the bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came from her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem that sodium hydroxide\Nwas mixed in with the lemon tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she drank it and then--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? There's something\Nfloating in the lemon tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a capsule!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So the perpetrator filled\Nthis capsule with sodium hydroxide,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then slipped it into the lemon tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then it would take time\Nfor the poison to be released,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making it impossible to determine\Nwhen the crime was committed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:10:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, any one of you six\Nwho entered her room
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,could have poisoned the tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!\NDoes that make me a suspect too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are capsules that dissolve in\Nhot water in only a few minutes' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Have the capsule analyzed at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say. How come you're not counting him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure he entered the room too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, a police superintendent\Nwould never poison his own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the boy's right. I'm a suspect\Njust as much as the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You do have a point...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nwe were recording a video!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! Did we\Nleave it on when we left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crime might've been caught on film!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still drink this sugary rubbish...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...That only I could ever make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still drinking this cheap filth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the actual poisoning\Nwasn't caught on tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though the video shows that nearly\Neveryone touched the can at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that everyone had\Nthe chance to poison the drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still watching it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Matsumoto-sensei's\Nsurgery is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poisoning her favorite lemon tea...\Nhow horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon tea, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time Sayuri drinks it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm reminded of a little girl\NI liked a lot a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always drank it with such happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I never even knew her name...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, he couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector. The results of\Nthe analysis have come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, assuming the capsule\Nwas added to the lemon tea,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would apparently take 15\Nto 16 minutes for it to dissolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15 to 16 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the poison was added
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at least 15 minutes\Nbefore she collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was 1:46 when\NRan-kun called the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming she collapsed to\Nthe floor one minute earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then that means the poison\Nwas added before 1:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was exactly 1:30 when\NSuperintendent Matsumoto left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which rules out both\Nthe groom and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to see\NMatsumoto-sensei after he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found something strange\Nabout the poisoned can...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The superintendent's fingerprints\Naren't anywhere on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can clearly see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I had the can in my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make a thorough check?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! The battery's almost out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! When Sonoko left...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she didn't have her can with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that she drank from...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, mister. Were the superintendent's\Nfingerprints the only ones missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that Umemiya person's\Nweren't on it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured as much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, where did\Nthat capsule come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I've figured out\Nthe culprit's intention!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the truth behind that capsule!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector. I found this in\Na trash can in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A glass jar...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like sodium hydroxide inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodium hydroxide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be the container the perpetrator\Nused when poisoning the tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodium hydroxide is a dangerous chemical
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that absorbs water in the air and\Nturns into a liquid in mere minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Send this for analysis too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was that bastard\Nwho smeared her dress with blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to see Matsumoto-sensei\Nat the hospital right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a little longer! We're not\Nfinished with our investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man Mori isn't around today,\Nso I'll need a pinch hitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now to match this voice changer\Nto Sonoko's voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured out who poisoned\NMatsumoto-sensei's lemon tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have, Sonoko-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that the perpetrator\Nput the poison capsule in her tea
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15 minutes before she collapsed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because it would take 15\Nto 16 minutes for the capsule to dissolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's assuming the poison\Nwas really in that capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.55,0:15:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we're sure of is that the capsule\Nwas floating in the poisoned lemon tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that the culprit--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.22,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The poison and the capsule\Nwere added in separately
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to fool us into thinking that the poison\Nwas added at least 15 minutes prior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, then you two\Ncould have done it as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. Everything she's\Nsaying is pure conjecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really might have\Nbeen a poison capsule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the video that Ran taped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector. Take a close look at\Nthe can of lemon tea on the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The labels are facing\Ndifferent directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran. Do you remember where I put\Nmy lemon tea when this happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in a hurry\Nso you put it on the table...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that your can?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason it looks\Nlike there's only one can
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is because the two cans\Nare perfectly lined up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She took my can, which just\Nhappened to be in front!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the poisoned can was devoid of\Nthe fingerprints of the superintendent
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Umemiya-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though they clearly\Nhad held the can earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd bet that my fingerprints\Nare on it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...That some time between her taking\Nthe wrong can and collapsing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:17:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone put the poison\Nand the capsule in separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And the only ones with her\Nat the time were Conan-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Takasugi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not to mention me and Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excluding Conan-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when Ran and I returned\Nfrom buying batteries,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasugi-san was holding the can\Nand then she took it from him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it would've been impossible\Nfor me or Ran to poison it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's the only one left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. There's one other person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto-sensei, herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suicide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if she did mix the poison in\Nto kill herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she would've added it shortly\Nbefore collapsing to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to do that,\Nshe would need two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An airtight container and a desiccant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes only a few minutes for\Nsodium hydroxide to turn to liquid
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when exposed to the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was in this room the entire time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she would have needed a\Ncontainer to safely store it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the container was found...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...In a trash can in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is proof that someone\Nother than Matsumoto-sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,brought the poison into this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the only one who could've slipped\Nthe poison into the lemon tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was you, Takasugi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toshihiko! How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why'd you do that to my daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna know so badly,\Nthen I'll tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all started 20 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a car that you were\Nchasing ran over my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was still alive at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She could've survived if you had\Nrushed her to the hospital in your car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,15 minutes later, my mother died,\Nlying on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:19:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From that day forth, I never once\Nforgot your cruel, heartless face!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he telling the truth, superintendent?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I didn't see her--she was\Nobscured by the car's shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later on, I learned of the accident\Nand rushed to his house,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he had already moved out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother was the only family I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was adopted by the Takasugi family\Nas they had no children of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then seven years ago,\NKazumi brought a girl with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The instant I learned\Nthat she was your daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my nearly-forgotten flames of\Nrevenge roared back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you died, you wouldn't get to\Nexperience how heartbreaking it is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to lose someone dear to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was one stupid girl, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had no clue I was getting\Nclose to her to get revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:20:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm sure being the heir\Nto the Takasugi fortune was--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who doesn't\Nhave a clue, Toshihiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayuri knew everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even about the accident\N20 years ago and your lineage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd never marry me\Nif she knew who I really was!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't get it, even after\Nseeing all that lemon tea she drinks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first boyfriend that\Nshe's always been thinking about
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the past 20 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.79,0:20:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayuri kept talking about\Nhow much you looked like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I did some investigating\Nand found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was really worried,\Neven after she accepted your proposal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't know what to do\Nto earn your forgiveness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you went and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she saw him\Npoison the drink?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knew it was poisoned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll be there soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superintendent! We just\Nreceived word from the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been upgraded to stable condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:51.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:22:00.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:05.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:11.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:21.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:29.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:35.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:45.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:49.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:23:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two months later, Matsumoto-sensei\Nchecked out of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that you got to leave\Nthe hospital earlier than expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I hear that Toshihiko-san's\Nsentence was reduced...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.34,0:23:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did drink the poison\Nof my own free will...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, it looks like I only\Nsucceeded in getting him in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he hates me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In celebration of leaving the hospital,\NI'll buy a drink for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lemon tea, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to\Ncherish memories of the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.19,0:23:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really now! If you keep this up,\Nyou'll never get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was married three years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.49,0:23:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Married to the one she had thought\Nabout for 20 long years, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.38,0:24:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you could\Npossibly be the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.17,0:24:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.94,0:24:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who just explained\Nwhy she couldn't have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.64,0:24:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Now I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an alibi trick\Ninvolving elevators!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.43,0:24:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.73,0:24:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Elevator Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.30,0:24:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.49,0:24:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bouquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.38,0:24:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode is another battle \Nagainst the culprit and their trick.
